Column.Name: Name
Column.ValidationFormula:
LET $match:= DB_LOOKUP( "Name", [EFormType], "[RecordID] <> " & DB_ENCODECONSTANT([RecordID])& " AND[LineNumber] FAST_EQUAL_TO 1 AND [Name] = "& DB_ENCODECONSTANT($thisValue), );
RETURN IF( $thisValue = NULL(), "Category name is required", $match <> NULL(), "A category record with the same name exists already", TRUE )
